OL,3,CPublic 'deserve better' as millions
OL,4,Cwasted on IT, top civil servant says
OL,6,FHe adds: "It's clear to me that there
OL,7,Fhas been significant waste across
OL,8,Fseveral major transformation projects.
OL,10,F"I have been especially concerned
OL,11,Fabout the first version of the MyGov
OL,12,Fprogramme. It was meant to digitise
OL,13,Fgovernment services, yet from
OL,14,Feverything I've seen, it delivered
OL,15,Fnothing of any substance. We need to
OL,16,Funderstand how that was allowed to
OL,17,Fhappen."
