OL,3,CPublic 'deserve better' as millions
OL,4,Cwasted on IT, top civil servant says
OL,6,FThese comments come after Deputy Gavin
OL,7,FSt Pier, the Vice-President of Policy
OL,8,Fand Resources, delivered a speech in
OL,9,Fthe States Assembly - publicly
OL,10,Frevealing the extent of money wasted.
OL,12,FA total of #42 million was invested to
OL,13,Fimprove government systems - #24
OL,14,Fmillion for the Revenue Service
OL,15,FTransformation project and #18 million
OL,16,Ffor 'MyGov' online services.
