OL,3,CPublic 'deserve better' as millions
OL,4,Cwasted on IT, top civil servant says
OL,6,F"The original MyGov programme ... fell
OL,7,Fsignificantly short of the progress
OL,8,Fand benefits that were promised. In
OL,9,Ffact, it appears there have been none.
OL,11,F"To this we can add the Electronic
OL,12,FPatient Record, which is running
OL,13,Fbehind schedule and budget, despite
OL,14,Freassurances.
OL,16,F"These failures represent an
OL,17,Funconscionable waste of public money.
OL,18,FThey have damaged trust and confidence
OL,19,Fin the Government's ability to deliver
OL,20,Fchange effectively. That is totally
OL,21,Funacceptable."
