OL,3,CPublic 'deserve better' as millions
OL,4,Cwasted on IT, top civil servant says
OL,6,FMr Smillie will create a team to
OL,7,Faddress the "underlying issues,
OL,8,Fstrengthen assurance at every stage,
OL,9,Fand rebuild confidence in the public
OL,10,Fservice's ability to actually deliver
OL,11,Fmajor change effectively".
OL,13,FThis includes examining in detail how
OL,14,Fmoney was spent on these major
OL,15,Fprojects, working out what is needed
OL,16,F"to fix failures and strengthen
OL,17,Fperformance", and ensuring
OL,18,Ftransparency throughout.
